#   - Sergey Belov + svgo team (svg/svgo)
#   - Matt Zabriskie + axios team (axios)
#   - Stuart Knightley (jszip)
#   - Justin Latimer (node-midi)
#
# Sebastian Raff (Hobbyquaker)'s smart-home
# ecosystem footprint (the hobbyquaker GitHub
# org) is also worth noting - he authored ~30+
# MQTT-bridge daemons that connect proprietary
# smart-home protocols (HomeMatic + Z-Wave +
# Zigbee + various manufacturer IoT clouds) to
# MQTT for unified Home Assistant integration.
# His position is in the *smart-home-bridge
# ecosystem-glue* vertical - distinct from
